text: Came here during 4am! And was surprised they're still open! Ordered Maggie soup and a glass of teh tarik. Awesome 👍🏼
I ordered maggie goreng ayam and I got maggie goreng ayam basi. How can you serve your customers spoiled food? It smelled so damn bad I puked on my first bite. Yuck!!!
Probably the worst mamak in our country. The roti maker are very slow like zombie.🤬😤
Loudzy service, customer waiting so long until fedup .. calling them also like act blur,.my suggestion is don't go this place for having lunch or dinner..very disappointed. 👎👎👎👎👎
